	&lt;li&gt;The famous Quit India Movement is also known as the&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;August Movement&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;. It was launched by Mahatma Gandhi on&lt;strong&gt; 8 August 1942&lt;/strong&gt; at Gowalia Tank Maidan, Bombay.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Gandhi Jee&amp;nbsp;raised the slogan&amp;nbsp;&amp;lsquo;&lt;strong&gt;do or die&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo; in his Quit India speech.&lt;/li&gt;
