&lt;p style=&quot;color:  (33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The correct answer is option &lt;b&gt;1&lt;/b&gt; i.e &lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Amartya Sen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

